column1:
Ooh... Agh... Oh yeah... This place is definitely
heaven...

The water is indeed divine. We must absorb all
the healing energy we can.
Y'know, I hope Gramps is all right.

The man is more dependable than he seems.
I'm willing to take him at his word.

We may not be waiting long. Once he gets
Konoe's keyword, we spring into action.
So be ready at a moment's notice.

That's the spirit! I knew I could count on you,
[1B]S1!

Well... Maybe not at this very moment.
Right now it's relax time.
Wow, it's so huge! And look how it's laid out!

Could this be a mixed bath? Maybe that's why
it's so empty.

It switches every so often. After eight o'clock,
it's women only.

The doors on the men's side should've
automatically closed.
Then I guess it's all ours.
Sweet! I'm gonna boil myself like an egg!
Why the hell are they here!?

We must have entered right when the time
allotment switched...
No, it's too late. They're already here.
WHERE!? No wait, that's even worse!

Calm down, boneheads. Our honor is at
stake here!

As noble thieves—as gentlemen—we need
to vanish without a trace!

Failing means certain death. Joker, let's begin
the operation!
Mmm, the water feels so good!
Ahh, I could stay here forever... Think I'm gonna melt.
